  "description": {
    "zh": "我们的哥们Victor需要我们帮忙做最后一件事。他需要一些地图来基本了解该地区的结构，一些地形测绘地图应该就可以了，但他也想知道如何在天蓝海岸的健康度假村导航，毕竟不是每个人都像你一样对那里了如指掌，对吧？有趣的家伙……\n\n总之，我刚刚说到哪了？哦，对了。他也需要一些钱，现金，西方货币。他说他可以用卢布支付大部分费用，我估计这对你来说不是大问题。所以你能把东西带来吗？",
    "en": "Our guy Victor wants our help with one last thing. He needs some maps to get a basic idea of how the area is structured, a few topographic survey maps should do just fine but he also wants to know how to navigate the health resort on the azure coast, after all not everyone knows the place in and out like you, right? Funny guy...\n\nAnyway, where was I again? Oh yeah, right. He needs some money too, cash, western currency. He said he can cover most of the cost in roubles, I assume that won't be a huge issue for you. So can you bring the stuff?"
  },
